versionText:
This topic branch adds a new ai model. This ai model is simulation based, so it plays every card in it's hand in a simulation of the game in order to find the best card.

THIS AI MODEL IS UNFINISHED. IT TAKES FOREVER, USES UP A LOT OF MEMORY, AND CURRENTLY THE ONLY NEW THINGS THE AI DOES IS PLAY CARDS, AND ATTACK. THE PREVIOUS MODEL DOES EVERYTHING ELSE.
